p.k: Gumball is late to meet Penny at the mall, but a series of misunderstandings on the way only delay him further. / When Mom sees Darwin gazing longingly at a fish-tank she thinks their mammalian lifestyle isn’t fulfilling her adopted son and deep down he longs to connect with his fishy roots. / The Parent Teacher Association of Elmore Junior High ban video games, so the kids try and prove that games aren’t a bad influence. / Tobias follows every single high-five with a butt-slap, so when Gumball doesn’t get one he feels insulted. / Gumball has to save Mr Robinson’s life during Elmore’s Senior Talent Show!
